		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I don't like the story as much as I like the world it takes place in. I had a lot more fun reading Harry Potter wikis than I ever did reading the books. All the backstory and little things created are really wonderful. It's really a great little world.
<br />
<br />I did enjoy the films, though I wouldn't try to convince you they're good.

		

