		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Haven't read the book. Watched all the movies, started only when 6th came out because everyone watched them. First two were really boring, 3rd was just great, all other were OK, except 6th that I liked too.
<br />
<br />I don't like Harry as a character, by the way, he is mostly like a void in the movies, he has no strong personality and not someone you can associate with yourself. Don't really like other two main characters, although they are definitely stronger. The world, mood, and especially supporting characters is what makes it interesting.

		

